  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with T2DM, diagnosed at least 3 months prior to Visit 1

          -  CHF (NYHA Class I, Class II, or Class III) at Visit 1

          -  LVEF &lt; 40%

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant or lactating female

          -  FPG ≥ 270 mg/dL (≥15 mmol/L)
      </textblock>
